### Seed demo data
POST http://localhost:8317/api/dev/seed

### List pets
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets

### Create pet
POST http://localhost:8317/api/pets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Milo",
  "species": "DOG",
  "breed": "Mixed breed",
  "sex": "UNKNOWN",
  "currentWeightKg": 18.4
}

### Replace PET_ID before using
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets/PET_ID/insights
